Image Prompt:
Create an ethereal and symbolic representation of God's divine plan unfolding, showcasing a serene and heavenly landscape with rays of light illuminating a path through the clouds. Include subtle elements like a gentle hand guiding the way and intricate patterns symbolizing the intricate workings of God's will. Convey a sense of awe and reverence, emphasizing the idea of perfection and purpose in every detail of creation.
